title: Insight Seminars Party
desc: We're coming toward the end of a fabulous year for Insight.?We want to celebrate and you're invited!? There will be dancing, a casino, silent auction, and tons of fun games. Bring your friends and family of all ages. Donating Auction Items: We're holding a silent auction at this event to raise funds for Youth Tuition Assistance. If you have something that would make a great auction item, please contact David Bloome at  davebloome@gmail.com . ?Thank you! Cost: Dancing and games are free. Casino chips are $25 per stack, which you can buy that night. Questions: specialevents@insightseminars.org ?or (800) 311-8001, ext 223.
